                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18171029-120-off641 t18171029-120-crimeloc643"></join>. On the 16th of October, I was at the counter, the rack at the door fell down - I ran out and saw the prisoner walking on; I called out, Brown stopped him with the pelisse under his arm.</p>
